data.description: Welcome to your new home in the tranquil subdivision Applewood Farms. This home has great space with a cozy split floorplan. Perfect location near Obici hospital with tons of dining and shopping close by. Interstate access makes a commute to Newport News, Norfolk, Portsmouth, Chesapeake a breeze. (20 minutes) Beautiful sunroom that leads to your back deck overlooking a peaceful wooded setting. You just might see deer! New roof(2023), brand new washer, newer dishwasher and microwave. Room above the garage can be 4th bedroom, office and/or study. Bright, airy neutral colors. Eat-in kitchen and dining room.
